   545→		// elements, so we'll always use an object here in case we've now made
   546→		// different elements have different types. Our ultimate goal is to
   547→		// marshal to JSON anyway, and all of these mapping types are
   548→		// indistinguishable in JSON.
   549→		return cty.ObjectVal(vals)
